import { FormControl, FormLabel, VStack } from '@chakra-ui/react'
import React from 'react'

const Signup = () => {
  return  <VStack spacing='5px'>
  <FormControl>
    <FormLabel></FormLabel>
    <Input
    placeholder="Enter your name"
    onChange></Input>
    /> 
  </FormControl>

  </VStack>
    
  
}

export default Signup
